    <main>
        <div class="flex items-stretch flex-wrap my-3 h-full">
            <div class="w-2/6">
                <CardColor color="red">
                    <Image class="" src={imgUser} alt="profile" />
                </CardColor>
            </div>
            <div class="w-4/6" >
                <CardColor color="blue">
                    <p class="text-4xl font-bold underline underline-offset-2 mb-2">@alfidibesta</p>
                    <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">
                        jr. web programer
                    </p>
                    <p class="font-normal text-normal">at Cranium</p>
                    <p class="text-xl font-normal">Located in Indonesia üáÆüá©</p>
                    <Button color="green" href="/blog">
                        <p class="text-base font-normal">
                            See more  
                            <span class="float-right">&rarr;</span>
                        </p>
                    </Button>
                </CardColor>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap my-3 h-full">
            <div class="flex-none w-full md:w-3/5">
                <CardColor color="yellow">
                    <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tentang Guweh üóø</p>
                    <p class="text-base font-normal">
                        I am Besta Alfidi, an Informatics Engineering student who has graduated at the State Polytechnic of Malang with GPA 3.53. Interested in UI/UX Designer and Graphic Design.
                        During lectures I honed interest in UI/UX Designer and Graphic Design by attending forums and courses.
                        I have high dedication in doing a task, diligent in learning and able to work under pressure this can be reflected during college in attending lectures and participation in organize. 
                        In Organization I really favor teamwork, the power of critical thinking and adaptive. 
                        With a travel background during college, I looked for opportunities to enter into the world UI/UX Designer to suit my background and interests.
                    </p>
                </CardColor>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-none w-full md:w-2/5">
                <CardColor color="yellow">
                    <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Lagi gabut belajar</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
                        {codingLanguages.map((button, index) => (
                                <Button color={button.color}>
                                    <p class="text-base font-normal">{button.text}</p>
                                </Button>
                        ))}
                    </div>
                </CardColor>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex my-3">
            <CardColor color="orange">
                <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Artikel yang baru baru üòÅ</p>
                <div class="flex flex-nowrap gap-3">
                    <div class="">
                        <CardBlog color="white" 
                        title={"Mulai ngoding.."} 
                        desc={"Interested in UI/UX Designer and Graphic Design."} 
                        link={"/blog"}>
                            <div class="aspect-video">
                                <Image class="bg-cover rounded-lg border-green-700 border-4" src={img1} alt="" />
                            </div>
                        </CardBlog>
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        <CardBlog color="white"
                        title={"Malas ngoding.."} 
                        desc={"Interested in UI/UX Designer and Graphic Design."} 
                        link={"/blog"}>
                            <div class="aspect-video">
                                <Image class="bg-cover rounded-lg border-green-700 border-4" src={img1} alt="" />
                            </div>
                        </CardBlog>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </CardColor>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap my-3">
            <CardColor color="blue">
                <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Follow ya...!</p>
                <div class="flex gap-3 flex-wrap container">
                    {socialMediaButtons.map((button, index) => (
                        <div class={`sosmed ${index === 0 ? 'active' : ''}`}>
                            <Button color={button.color}>
                                <p class="text-base font-normal">{button.text}</p>
                            </Button>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </CardColor>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>